import React, {Component} from "react"; export default class PaymentHistory extends Component { // Konstruktor //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { payments: [], } } // Získání dat //////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// componentDidMount() { let date = new Date(); // Request fetch("http://localhost:8080/api/payments/" + this.props.userID + "/year=" + date.getFullYear() + "&month=" + (date.getMonth() + 1)) .then(response => response.json().then(data => this.setState({ payments: data, }))); const payment = { id: 20, name: "TEST", amount: "-2 000,50", currencry: "CZK", variableSymbol: 1234567890, constantSymbol: 1234, specificSymbol: 5987654321, paymentDate: "03.08.2020" } } // Vykreslení ////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// render() { let year = new Date().getFullYear(); return(
{this.state.payments.map((item, index) =>
{item.paymentDate.replace(year, "")}
{item.name}
{item.amount} {item.currency}
{item.paymentType}
Variabilní symbol: {item.variableSymbol}
Konstantní symbol: {item.constantSymbol}
Specifický symbol: {item.specificSymbol}
ID transakce: {item.id}
Datum platby: {item.paymentDate}
)}
) } }
